data.description: Grab It while You Can. Captivating Ranch One Floor Living Has It All, Enjoy The Huge Sunny Yard For Entertaining, Room For A Pool! Extra Side Yard Perfect For Dog Run. The Living Room Has Stunning Wood Burning Fireplace. Cook Your Favorite Meals In Your Brand New Kitchen with Granite counters & Double Wall Oven. Master Bedroom With Full Bath And Large Closets. Two Additional Bedrooms And Full Bath. Step Into Your Sunken Extra-Large Family Room/Den For All Your Needs- Easy To Convert To 4th Bedroom. This Home Boasts A Partially Full Finished Basement With OSE For Clients Or Home Office, Separate Heat, And Blueprint Already In For Summer Kitchen. Private Driveway W Pavers & Parking For 4 Cars. New Vinyl Siding & Fence. Lots Of Natural Light. A Hidden Gem In The Heart Oceanside! Near Stores, Restaurants, Golf, Atlantic Ocean And LIRR Minutes Away. Low Priced Flood Insurance Is Transferable. Spacious Interior. Don't Wait, Low Market Inventory. Tons of recent updates...New fridge and dishwasher, New hot water heater, new lighting, New exterior trim and gutters, new bay window in front and rear of house, new electric service!
